#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga"
msgstr "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Uttarasutta"
msgstr "19. With Uttara"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.19:1.1"
msgid "Rājagahanidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Rājagaha."

msgctxt "sn2.19:1.2"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho uttaro devaputto bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Standing to one side, the god Uttara recited this verse in the Buddha’s "
"presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.55"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.126"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.19:2.1"
msgid "“Upanīyati jīvitamappamāyu,"
msgstr "“This life, so very short, is led onward."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.19:2.2"
msgid "Jarūpanītassa na santi tāṇā;"
msgstr "There’s no shelter for someone who’s been led on by old age."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.19:2.3"
msgid "Etaṃ bhayaṃ maraṇe pekkhamāno,"
msgstr "Seeing this peril in death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.19:2.4"
msgid "Puññāni kayirātha sukhāvahānī”ti."
msgstr "you should do good deeds that bring happiness.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.19:3.1"
msgid "“Upanīyati jīvitamappamāyu,"
msgstr "“This life, so very short, is led onward."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.19:3.2"
msgid "Jarūpanītassa na santi tāṇā;"
msgstr "There’s no shelter for someone who’s been led on by old age."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.19:3.3"
msgid "Etaṃ bhayaṃ maraṇe pekkhamāno,"
msgstr "Seeing this peril in death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.19:3.4"
msgid "Lokāmisaṃ pajahe santipekkho”ti."
msgstr "one looking for peace would drop the world’s bait.”"
